abstract: Andrew Yang is showing what healthy populism looks like.
snippet: Andrew Yang is showing what healthy populism looks like.
lead_paragraph: It was New Year’s Eve, and I had decided to spend it with Andrew Yang. A self-described “Asian man who’s good at math,” Mr. Yang had raised an impressive $16.5 million in the fourth quarter of 2019 for his presidential campaign. Despite being newly flush, the campaign didn’t hold its shindig in a Napa Valley wine cave or at Gramercy Tavern, but in a fluorescent-lit room above a bar in Nashua, N.H.

abstract: It was President Trump’s second rally in three nights this week.
snippet: It was President Trump’s second rally in three nights this week.
lead_paragraph: Four Democratic presidential candidates hoping for breakout performances in the Iowa caucuses next week spent Thursday in Washington listening to questioning in the Senate impeachment trial of President Trump.
headline_main: Trump heads to Iowa in a bid to rally supporters for caucuses.

abstract: Four Democratic presidential candidates hoping for success in the state remained in Washington for President Trump’s Senate trial.
snippet: Four Democratic presidential candidates hoping for success in the state remained in Washington for President Trump’s Senate trial.
lead_paragraph: DES MOINES — Four Democratic presidential candidates hoping for breakout performances in the Iowa caucuses next week spent Thursday in Washington listening to questioning in the Senate impeachment trial of President Trump.
